text: Sergey Yanin (born 14 October 1953) is a Soviet ski jumper. He competed in the large hill event at the 1972 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of the Soviet Union Category:Ski jumpers at the 1972 Winter Olympics Category:People from Sverdlovsk
